<%= form_tag '/games', method: :post do %>

Fill out the following form to add a game to the list:
<div>
  <%= label_tag :name, "Game Title:" %>
  <%= text_field_tag :name %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= label_tag :price, "Price:" %>
  <%= text_field_tag :price %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= label_tag :description, "Description:" %>
  <%= text_field_tag :description %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= label_tag :image, "Image:" %>
  <%= text_field_tag :image %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= submit_tag "Submit Game" %>
</div>

<% end %>